               <head>PENITENTIAL WORKS, HONORIUS AUGUSTODUNENSIS, &amp;c. ; S. XIII, XIV 1/4 </head>
               <msContents>
                  <textLang mainLang="la" otherLangs="xno">Latin with a very little Anglo-Norman (accompanying material)</textLang>
