                        <title key="work_14583">Sermon</title>
                        <rubric>Sermo beati Ieronimi ad Paulam et Eustochium de penitencia Teophili</rubric>
                        <incipit>Factum est priusquam <sic>mencsio</sic> fieret in romanam rem pupplicam execrande Persarum gentis fuisse</incipit>
                        <explicit>uiuos et mortuos iudicaturo occisurum. Cui ...</explicit>
                        <note>Unauthentic. unpr.; Lambert 615, citing six copies, four of them English, though the earliest of the six (Milan, Bibl. Ambros. L. 28. Sup., s. x), is presumably Italian. </note>
